title: FUNK - GETT OFF YUR FAT Part 2 Selected By Rock Savage
description:
Funk - Gett Off Yur Fat Part 2

85 Funk Tracks compiled and selected by Rock Savage

This is not your average compilation, included here are some very rare Funk cuts recorded directly from the original vinyl. All others are from the original source.

Artists include Marvin Gaye, Betty Davis, Ohio Players, Parliament, The Meters, Don Blackman, Roy Ayres, Earth Wind and Fire, Kool and the Gang and many more.

Mp3 192 and 256 kbps Format and Tagged. Original Artwork included.

It is time to get ya Funk on

Enjoy!
